com.esri.mo2.data.feat
Interface Lock

public interface Lock

Implements a Cache that can temporarily lock data to prevent deprecation during some significant operation, such as data retrieval. YOu can release the lock, once it is no longer required.

Method Summary
 void release()
          Releases the data managed by this Lock and allows subsequent deprecation.
